reviewText: Move beyond your current reality. This DVD is so awesome. It really opens the mind and makes you think differently!
The description of this DVD says 70 minutes.  I received it today, and the actual DVD claims 28 minutes.  Not hardly worth the money, no matter what the message.

PROS:  Visuals are pretty.  Meditation session is relaxing.
CONS:  You blink and it is over.  4 short sections:  Now Is The Time, Humanitarians of Light; Guided Meditation; and Awakening.
You really don't meet Panache Desai.  Not worth the $16.00 for dvd.
